com.vangav.backend.play_framework.controllers_generator.json

Class RequestParamJson

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vangav.backend.play_framework.controllers_generator.json.RequestParamJson

  • public class RequestParamJson
extends java.lang.Object
    RequestParamJson is the json representation of a controller's request param e.g.: name: latitude type: LATITUDE (double) is_array: false optionality: MANDATORY

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      boolean is_array
      is_array is true if this param is an array and false otherwise
      java.lang.String name
      name represents the param name
      java.lang.String optionality
      optionality is MANDATORY or OPTIONAL, MANDATORY params stop the request and return BadRequest 400 code if the param isn't valid while OPTIONAL params don't stop the request if they are invalid
      java.lang.String type
      type represents the param type (e.g.: FB_ID, ALTITUDE, E_MAIL, etc ...)
